snippet.title: Obduction Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Obduction. New worlds, from the creators of Myst and Riven.

(This trailer may contain spoilers.)

As you walk through the woods on a pristine night, a curious, organic artifact falls from the starry sky and inexplicably, without asking permission, moves you across the universe. The answer to your questions about where you are, and why you’re here, lie ahead. This is your story now.
